---
const mailto =
  "mailto:info@affinitylab.it?subject=Richiesta%20demo%20SofIA&body=Ciao%2C%20vorrei%20una%20demo%20di%20SofIA%20per%20la%20mia%20attivit%C3%A0.";
---

<section class="section cta" id="prova">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta__box" data-reveal>
      <span class="cta__grid" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <div class="cta__content">
        <span class="pill"><span class="dot-live"></span> Demo live · 3 minuti gratis</span>
        <h2 class="cta__title">Parla con SofIA. Adesso.</h2>
        <p class="cta__lead">
          Non leggere come funziona: provala. Scegli uno scenario e fai una
          chiamata vera, direttamente dal browser.
        </p>
        <div class="cta__actions">
          <button class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" data-trial-open>
            <span class="dot-live"></span> Avvia la prova gratuita
          </button>
          <a href={mailto} class="btn btn--inverted btn--lg">Richiedi una demo</a>
        </div>
        <p class="cta__note">Nessun impegno · Nessuna carta · Voce naturale multilingua</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta__box {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: clamp(2.5rem, 1.5rem + 5vw, 5.5rem) var(--gutter);
    background: linear-gradient(150deg, var(--coral) 0%, var(--coral-700) 100%);
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  .cta__grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
    mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #000, transparent 72%);
    -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #000, transparent 72%);
  }
  .cta__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.1rem;
    justify-items: center;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  .cta .pill {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    color: #fff;
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  }
  .cta .pill .dot-live {
    background: #fff;
  }
  .cta__title {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: var(--step-4);
  }
  .cta__lead {
    font-size: var(--step-1);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
  }
  .cta__actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 0.4rem;
  }
  .cta__actions .btn--primary {
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--coral-700);
  }
  .cta__actions .btn--primary:hover {
    background: var(--cream);
  }
  .cta__note {
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
